Monné (2018c) and 
<bibRefCitation author="Tavakilian, G. &amp; Chevillotte, H." box="[424,781,1639,1665]" pageId="1" pageNumber="521" refId="ref7297" refString="Tavakilian, G. &amp; Chevillotte, H. (2018) Titan: base de donnees internationales sur les Cerambycidae ou Longicornes. Version 3.0. Available from: http: // titan. gbif. fr / (accessed 31 January 2019)" type="url" year="2018">Tavakilian &amp; Chevillotte (2018)</bibRefCitation>
